lear reporting of their portfolio holdings transactions performance and fees we have gleaned valuable insights and best practices over the past  years acting as a fiduciary and investment advisor to some of the country’s biggest retirement plans that we can apply to your wealth planning and investment challenges our size provides us with access to bestinclass investment managers that we couple with customized planning services delivered by experienced financial advisors our conflictfree business model means that our advisors’ interests are aligned with yours they have no products to sell and are in a position to offer truly objective advice resources   global markets’ midyear momentum   find your tribe   the surprising benefits of a  fiduciary recognition captrust again named  us advisory firm the july  issue of financial advisor magazine ranked captrust number one among registered investment advisors rias with assets in excess of  billion—making it our second year running to achieve this distinction the magazine’s annual survey analyzes several metrics and other indicators of business success read more announcements vested summer  we are pleased to announce that the summer  issue of vested captrust’s magazine for clients and friends is now available subscribing clients will receive their copies in the mail the week of june  if you are interested in receiving vested magazine please contact your captrust financial advisor or let us know via email read more recognition captrust’s goldstein honored as outstanding csuite level executive captrust chief operating officer ben goldstein was recognized by the triangle business journal in its inaugural csuite awards recognizing the best of the best in corporate leadership in the triangle who have made significant impact on the success of their organizations read more captrust advisor finder search for a captrust advisor by name or primary office location start search captrust advisors  institutional investors retirement plans